  "title": "Sales & Marketing Officer (Basic + High Comms)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Title:</strong> Sales &amp; Marketing Officer (Basic + High Comms)</p>\n<p><strong>Location:</strong> Island-wide / Multiple Branches</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>About the Role:</strong><br>\nOur client is seeking enthusiastic Sales &amp; Marketing Officers to join their branch network across Singapore! In this role, you will engage with potential customers directly at bank branches or venues, promoting banking products, driving customer acquisition, and contributing to the branch’s outreach initiatives. This is ideal for individuals who enjoy interacting with people and achieving measurable results.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Promote and market banking products to potential customers at various bank branches and/or roadshows</li>\n  <li>Build relationships with customers and drive acquisition targets.</li>\n  <li>Support branch activations, roadshows, and community engagement events.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with marketing and sales teams to execute campaigns effectively.</li>\n  <li>Track and report performance metrics, providing insights to enhance engagement strategies.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum <strong>N-level qualification with at least 3 passes</strong>.</li>\n  <li>Fluent in English with excellent communication skills.</li>\n  <li>Strong interpersonal skills; confident engaging with diverse customers.</li>\n  <li>Target-driven, self-motivated, and resilient in a fast-paced environment.</li>\n  <li>Able and willing to be stationed at multiple bank branches across the island.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What’s on Offer:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Competitive salary with performance-based incentives.</li>\n  <li>Hands-on experience in customer engagement and acquisition.</li>\n  <li>Opportunities to connect with diverse customer segments and grow professionally.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We appreciate your interest and look forward to reviewing your application. Due to high application volume, only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>WeCruit Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0270</strong><br>\n<strong>EA Personnel:</strong> Tan Soon Hock (Steven) | Registration No. R1109889</p>",
